    "longBusinessSummary": "Sao Vang Rubber Joint Stock Company manufactures and trades rubber products in Vietnam. It offers car tires, tube, and apron; truck and bus, light truck and small bus, agricultural, and special tires; motorcycle tube, and tubeless and with-tube tires; electrified bicycle inner tube and tires; and aircraft inner tube and tires, as well as tires for bicycles, carts, and mountain bike. In addition, it sells technical rubber products, such as rubber conveyor belts, technical rubber parts, rubber hoses, rubber roller and anti-collision, cushions, and other products. Further, the company provides leasing services, including shops, offices, factories, and warehouses. Additionally, it engages in the import and export of materials, machinery, equipment, and chemicals for the rubber industry, as well as in the trading of automotive spare parts and coal. The company was founded in 1960 and is headquartered in Hanoi, Vietnam.",
